CustomField.description: The counrty code of the user that made or received the call. For example, UK would be 44.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This is the home country code of the Natterbox user involved in the call. This is the 2 or 3 digit numeric dialling code for that country. For example, for the UK, this would be '44'.
CustomField.label: HomeCountryCode
